        <updateDate>2007-09-14T18:17:41Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Internal Revenue Code to allow the issuance of tax-exempt facility bonds through 2012 to make automobile development and production facilities built before 1981 compatible for the development and production of qualified alternative motor vehicles and component parts.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
